<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.4.1">
<l>nilaiyiṭa meṅku miṉṟi neṭuveḷḷa mumpar vaḷanāṭu mūṭa vimaiyōr</l>
<l>talaiyiṭa maṟṟe makkōr caraṇillai yeṉṉa varaṇāva ṉeṉṉu maruḷāl</l>
<l>alaikaṭal nīrkku ḻampa vakaṭāṭa vōṭi yakalvāṉu riñca mutukil</l>
<l>malaikaḷai mītu koṇṭu varumīṉai mālai maṟavāti ṟaiñceṉ maṉaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, bow down without fail to Māl,</l>
<l rend="indent">the fish which brought mountains on its back</l>
<l rend="indent">as it scraped the broad heavens,</l>
<l>Speeding as its belly wriggled, so that the crashing sea tossed up water,</l>
<l rend="indent">by the grace of saying, “I will be [your] protection,”</l>
<l>When a vast flood, without any fixed place,</l>
<l rend="indent">concealed the gods’ prosperous land,</l>
<l>When the unblinking [celestials] cried, “Without a place with a summit,</l>
<l rend="indent">there is no refuge for us.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
